It's true that many of those who speak these languages already know another more common language,

00:05:43.980 --> 00:05:46.980
to be able to converse with others.

00:05:46.980 --> 00:05:54.980
So why go to all the trouble of translating the Bible's message into these less common languages?

00:05:54.980 --> 00:06:00.980
