00:06:00.980 --> 00:06:07.980
To have a God Himself set the example by what He did on the day of Pentecost in the year 33CE.

00:06:08.980 --> 00:06:14.980
You might remember that He miraculously enabled the crowds of visitors there in Jerusalem to hear the message

00:06:14.980 --> 00:06:22.980
