00:07:00.980 --> 00:07:07.980
How it strengthens our faith to know that our loving Heavenly Father desires that all sorts of persons

00:07:07.980 --> 00:07:10.980
have an opportunity to hear the truth about Him.

00:07:10.980 --> 00:07:18.980
And what a privilege we have to be associated with an organization that is helping people of all language groups

00:07:18.980 --> 00:07:22.980
large and small to do exactly that.
